ABOUT CHEMTECH

Chemtech is a SIEMENS company in Brazil and has sponsored the development
of this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

CAM::PDF

COPYRIGHT AND LICENCE

Copyright (C) 2009 by Donato Azevedo
